                    <h3>Optimized compute: latest generation CPU</h3>
                    <p>Dv2-series instances are the next generation of D-series instances. They can be used as Virtual Machines or Cloud Services. Dv2-series instances will carry more powerful CPUs and the same memory and disk configurations as the D-series. Dv2-series instances are based on the latest generation 2.4 GHz Intel Xeon® E5-2673 v3 (Haswell) processor, and can go to 3.2 GHz with Intel Turbo Boost Technology 2.0. The Dv2-series and D-series are ideal for applications that demand faster CPUs, better local disk performance, or higher memories, and offer a powerful combination for many enterprise-grade applications.</p>
